prediction.sparql:
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?series ?seriesLabel ( COUNT( ?ep ) AS ?episodeCount ) ?numVotes WHERE {
  ?series imdb:numVotes ?numVotes .
  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?numVotes ) > 1000000 ) .
  ?ep imdb:parentTitle ?series .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?series rdfs:label ?seriesLabel
  }
}
GROUP BY ?series ?seriesLabel ?numVotes
ORDER BY DESC ( ?episodeCount )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?decadeStart ( xsd:decimal ( AVG( ?rating ) ) AS ?avgRating ) ( COUNT( ?movie ) AS ?movieCount ) WHERE {
  ?movie rdf:type imdb:Movie .
  ?movie imdb:genre ?genre .
  FILTER ( regex( str( ?genre ) , "Sci[- ]?Fi" , "i" ) ) ?movie imdb:averageRating ?rating .
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?numVotes .
  FILTER ( ?numVotes > 10000 ) ?movie imdb:startYear ?startYear .
  BIND( floor( ?startYear / 10 ) AS ?decadeFloor ) BIND( xsd:int ( ?decadeFloor * 10 ) AS ?decadeStart )
}
GROUP BY ?decadeStart
ORDER BY ?decadeStart

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?series ( SAMPLE( ?seriesLabel ) AS ?label ) ( AVG( xsd:decimal ( ?rating ) ) AS ?avgRating ) ( COUNT( ?ep ) AS ?epCount ) WHERE {
  ?ep imdb:parentTitle ?series .
  ?ep imdb:episodeNumber ?epNum .
  ?ep imdb:averageRating ?rating .
  ?ep imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?votes ) >= 10000 ) OPTIONAL {
    ?series rdfs:label ?seriesLabel
  }
}
GROUP BY ?series
HAVING ( COUNT( ?ep ) >= 20 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?avgRating )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX imdb_principal: <https://www.imdb.com/principal/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personLabel WHERE {
  ?actorTitle imdb_principal:actor ?person .
  ?actorTitle imdb:numVotes ?votes1 .
  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?votes1 ) > 100000 ) ?directorTitle imdb_principal:director ?person .
  ?directorTitle imdb:numVotes ?votes2 .
  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?votes2 ) > 100000 ) FILTER ( ?actorTitle != ?directorTitle ) OPTIONAL {
    ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel
  }
}
ORDER BY ?personLabel

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?person ( SAMPLE( ?plabel ) AS ?personLabel ) ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) AS ?titleCount ) ( AVG( xsd:double ( ?numVotes ) ) AS ?avgVotes ) WHERE {
  ?title ?role ?person .
  FILTER ( STRSTARTS( STR( ?role ) , "https://www.imdb.com/principal/" ) ) ?title imdb:numVotes ?numVotes .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?person rdfs:label ?plabel
  }
}
GROUP BY ?person
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) >= 3 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?avgVotes )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?series ( SAMPLE( ?label ) AS ?seriesLabel ) ( SAMPLE( xsd:integer ( ?seriesVotes ) ) AS ?seriesVotesSample ) ( MAX( xsd:integer ( ?epRuntime ) ) AS ?maxRuntime ) ( MIN( xsd:integer ( ?epRuntime ) ) AS ?minRuntime ) ( ( MAX( xsd:integer ( ?epRuntime ) ) - MIN( xsd:integer ( ?epRuntime ) ) ) AS ?runtimeDiff ) WHERE {
  ?episode imdb:parentTitle ?series .
  ?episode imdb:runtimeMinutes ?epRuntime .
  ?series imdb:numVotes ?seriesVotes .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?series rdfs:label ?label .
  }
  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?seriesVotes ) > 100000 )
}
GROUP BY ?series
ORDER BY DESC ( ?runtimeDiff )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?person ( SAMPLE( ?personLabel ) AS ?personLabelSample ) ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?person imdb:knownForTitle ?title .
  ?title imdb:numVotes ?numVotes .
  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?numVotes ) > 1000000 ) OPTIONAL {
    ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel
  }
}
GROUP BY ?person
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) >= 3 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
LIMIT 200
